summary: A large Player owned home build in the cracks above riverwood. includes Blacksmiths\'s set (Forge, Smelter, workbench, Grindstone and tanning rack) and mage\'s set (Alchemy, enchanting Table).
descriptionHtml:
Adds a player owned home build in the craks of the mautains above riverwood, it\'s nothing special from the outside but that\'s why it\'s better on the inside. you have everything you need plus a bit more :D its visible on the map so it should be easy to find.
please report any bugs so i can fix them !! 

Rooms:
Entrance Hall
Living Quaters
Smithy 
Treasury
Kitchen
Dinning Room
Mage Quaters
Military Quaters


Installastion:
just copy all the files in your skyrim data folder.
and fell free to upload images !!

NOTE: special thanks to Oaristys & tony 67 for awsome meshes !!!!
author: Alduin1998
